hands_on_practices.solution:
1. External complex potential derivative at $z_0$ (without the self-vortex) is  
$$\frac{d\mathcal{W}_{\text{ext}}}{dz}\Big|_{z_0}
=\frac{d}{dz}\Big[U\big(z+\frac{a^2}{z}\big)\Big]_{z_0}
+\frac{d}{dz}\Big[-\,\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\ln(z-z_1)\Big]_{z_0}
+\frac{d}{dz}\Big[\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\ln z\Big]_{z_0}\,. $$
2. Compute each term at $z_0=i k a$ ($k>1$):  
   a) Uniform stream past cylinder:  
   $$\frac{d}{dz}\Big[U(z+\frac{a^2}{z})\Big]
   =U\Big(1-\frac{a^2}{z^2}\Big)
   \quad\Rightarrow\quad
   U\Big(1+\frac1{k^2}\Big)
   =U\frac{k^2+1}{k^2}\,. $$
   b) Image vortices: $z_1=a^2/\bar z_0=i a/k$.  
   $$\frac{d}{dz}\Big[-\,\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\ln(z-z_1)\Big]_{z_0}
   =-\,\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi(z_0-z_1)},\quad
   \frac{d}{dz}\Big[\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\ln z\Big]_{z_0}
   =\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi z_0}\,. $$
   Compute
   $$\frac1{z_0}=-\frac{i}{k a},\quad
   \frac1{z_0-z_1}
   =-\frac{i\,k}{a(k^2-1)},$$
   so
   $$\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\Big(\frac1{z_0}-\frac1{z_0-z_1}\Big)
   =\frac{i\Gamma}{2\pi}\cdot\frac{i}{a\,k(k^2-1)}
   =-\frac{\Gamma}{2\pi\,a\,k(k^2-1)}\,. $$
3. Stagnation condition $\displaystyle\frac{d\mathcal{W}_{\text{ext}}}{dz}\Big|_{z_0}=0$ gives  
$$U\frac{k^2+1}{k^2}
-\frac{\Gamma}{2\pi\,a\,k(k^2-1)}=0
\quad\Longrightarrow\quad
\frac{\Gamma}{Ua}
=2\pi\,\frac{k(k^2-1)(k^2+1)}{k^2}
=2\pi\,\frac{k^4-1}{k}\,. $$
